Liberty Swing Dance Championships 2014

June 26 - 29
It’s our ten year anniversary!! Come help us celebrate Liberty Swing Dance Championships June 26 – 29, 2014 at the Hyatt Regency, New Brunswick, NJ. You can book your room now. The rate is $129 per night (Yes, it’s cheaper than last year!). To book your room, use https://resweb.passkey.com/Resweb.do?mode=welcome_ei_new&eventID=10708789 Ticket pricing will be available shortly.
